metadata.name: Smugbunny Hearts Shontelle
metadata.description: Smugbunny, the ultimate fashionista bunny, is taking the world by storm with a daring new collaboration alongside the one and only Bajan musician, Shontelle. With hearts in their eyes, Smugbunny rocks a bright red suit that screams both Valentine's Day and Shontelle's experimental flair. But wait, there's more! The suit features inflatable fabrics, making it a true masterpiece by Smugbunny's creator, JC. Get ready to witness a fashion moment like no other with Smugbunny and Shontelle in a one of a kind animation!
